        parsed_args={
            'prompt': 'Describe the segment reporting structure, segment definitions, and how revenue and costs are allocated across Space, Connectivity, and AI segments in {{spacex_s1}}. Include any discussion of shared resources, transfer pricing, or intersegment arrangements.'
